OL,3,CRetrial set for man accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering 'good Samaritan'
OL,6,FA man accused of murdering a 'good
OL,7,FSamaritan', who was killed while
OL,8,Fhelping a stranger lying in the
OL,9,Fstreet, will face a retrial next year.
OL,11,FFather-of-two Chris Marriott was
OL,12,Fgiving aid to Nafeesa Jhangur when a
OL,13,Fcar ploughed into a crowd of people on
OL,14,FCollege Close in the Burngreave area
OL,15,Fof Sheffield on December 27.
OL,17,FThe 46-year-old was among five people
OL,18,Fhit by the Seat Ibiza car, which was
OL,19,Fbeing driven by Ms Jhangur's brother,
OL,20,FHassan Jhangur, 24, Sheffield Crown
OL,21,FCourt heard earlier this year.
