OL,4,Cmurdering 'good Samaritan'
OL,6,FJhangur then got out of the vehicle
OL,7,Fand attacked another man with a knife,
OL,8,Fleaving him with serious injuries. The
OL,9,Fman he stabbed was Hasan Khan, who had
OL,10,Fmarried his sister Amaani earlier that
OL,11,Fday.
OL,13,FJhangur went on trial earlier this
OL,14,Fyear after denying murdering Mr
OL,15,FMarriott and a number of other
OL,16,Foffences relating to the incident,
OL,17,Fincluding the attempted murder of Mr
OL,18,FKhan.
