OL,3,CRetrial set for man accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering 'good Samaritan'
OL,6,FJhangur told his trial he lost control
OL,7,Fof the car as he went round a corner
OL,8,Fand did not intend to hurt those he
OL,9,Fhit. He said he stabbed Mr Khan as he
OL,10,Fdefended himself when he came under
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FAfter a week of deliberations, the
OL,14,Fjury was discharged after failing to
OL,15,Freach any verdicts.
OL,17,FOn Monday (August 12), a brief hearing
OL,18,Fat Sheffield Crown Court heard how
OL,19,FJhangur will face a retrial on all the
OL,20,Fcharges on June 4 2025.
