OL,3,CRetrial set for man accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering 'good Samaritan'
OL,6,FJhangur, of Whiteways Road, Sheffield,
OL,7,Fdenies the murder and manslaughter of
OL,8,FMr Marriott but he has pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fto causing Mr Marriott's death by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving.
OL,12,FHe had also admitted causing serious
OL,13,Finjury to Alison Norris, Ambreen
OL,14,FJhangur, Nafeesa Jhangur and Riasat
OL,15,FKhan by dangerous driving.
OL,17,FJhangur denies attempting to murder
OL,18,FHasan Khan and wounding him with
OL,19,Fintent.
