OL,6,FThe defendant has also pleaded not
OL,7,Fguilty to four charges of causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent.
OL,10,FJhangur will face a retrial alongside
OL,11,Fhis father, Mohammed Jhangur, 56, of
OL,12,FWhiteways Road, Sheffield, who denies
OL,13,Fa charge of perverting the course of
OL,14,Fjustice, which relates to him
OL,15,Fallegedly concealing a knife.
